description: Paul Rusesabagina, a hotel manager, houses over a thousand Tutsi refugees during their struggle against the Hutu militia in Rwanda, Africa.

description: A guy relies on his newly-acquired gladiator skills to save his ex-girlfriend from kidnappers.

description: World-renowned civil rights defense attorney Bryan Stevenson works to free a wrongly condemned death row prisoner.

description: A retiring assassin suddenly finds himself on the receiving end of a hit, contracted by none other than his own employer seeking to cash in on the pensions of aging employees.

description: A late night talk show host suspects that she may soon lose her long-running show.

description: A soon-to-be stepmom is snowed in with her fiancé's two children at a remote holiday village. Just as relations begin to thaw between the trio, some strange and frightening events take place.

description: Kazakh TV talking head Borat is dispatched to the United States to report on the greatest country in the world. With a documentary crew in tow, Borat becomes more interested in locating and marrying Pamela Anderson.

description: A couple tries to spice up their marriage in a remote lake house. After the husband dies unexpectedly, the wife is left handcuffed to their bed frame and must fight to survive and break free.

description: A holiday romantic comedy that captures the range of emotions tied to wanting your family's acceptance, being true to yourself, and trying not to ruin Christmas.

description: After swapping bodies with a deranged serial killer, a high-school senior discovers that she has fewer than 24 hours before the change becomes permanent.

description: Stuck in a time loop, two wedding guests develop a budding romance while living the same day over and over again.

name: Rama Shama Bhama
description: Must watch for who loves comedy in simple track Rama had best life with his wife.once he went to buy a new flat , he falls in love with priya. After they went to goa trip , Rama faces a lot of troubles

name: Revolver

name: Serenity
description: The crew of the ship Serenity try to evade an assassin sent to recapture telepath River.

description: A young man realizes that he has to push back against his domineering father if he wants to find true happiness and love.

description: A depressed wealthy businessman finds his life changing after he meets a spunky and care-free young woman.

name: Juno
description: Faced with an unplanned pregnancy, an offbeat young woman makes a selfless decision regarding the unborn child.

name: Milana
description: Hero is in love with a girl who is forced to marry a police officer. Hero is later forced by his parents to marry a girl of their choice, and she ends up wanting a divorce from him. Will he...                See full summary »

name: Mr. Brooks
description: A well-respected businessman is sometimes controlled by his murder and mayhem-loving alter ego.

description: Teen detective Nancy Drew accompanies her father on a business trip to Los Angeles, where she happens upon clues to a murder mystery involving a movie star.

description: A Las Vegas magician who can see into the future is pursued by FBI agents seeking to use his abilities to prevent a nuclear terrorist attack.

name: Teeth

name: The Game Plan

name: The Golden Compass

name: Doubt

name: Gaalipata

name: Hancock

name: Horton Hears a Who!

name: Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull

name: Iron Man

name: Jaane Tu... Ya Jaane Na

name: Kung Fu Panda

name: Låt den rätte komma in

name: Martyrs

name: Mirrors

name: Quantum of Solace

name: Quarantine

name: Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi

name: Freakdog

name: Restraint

name: Role Models

name: Seven Pounds
description: A man with a fateful secret embarks on an extraordinary journey of redemption by forever changing the lives of seven strangers.

name: Sex Drive

name: Slumdog Millionaire

name: Step Brothers

name: Taken
description: A retired CIA agent travels across Europe and relies on his old skills to save his estranged daughter, who has been kidnapped while on a trip to Paris.

name: The Alphabet Killer

name: The Boy in the Striped Pajamas

name: The Children

name: The Chronicles of Narnia: Prince Caspian

name: The Hurt Locker

name: The Incredible Hulk

name: The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants 2

name: Untraceable

name: Vantage Point

A rag doll that awakens in a postapocalyptic future holds the key to humanity's salvation.

name: (500) Days of Summer

name: Adventureland

name: An Education
description: A coming-of-age story about a teenage girl in 1960s suburban London, and how her life changes with the arrival of a playboy nearly twice her age.

name: A Serious Man
description: Larry Gopnik, a Midwestern physics teacher, watches his life unravel over multiple sudden incidents. Though seeking meaning and answers amidst his turmoils, he seems to keep sinking.

name: Avatar

name: Coraline

name: Daybreakers

name: Defendor

name: District 9

name: Drag Me to Hell

name: Fired Up!

name: Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince

name: My Sister's Keeper

name: Orphan

name: Sherlock Holmes

name: Star Trek

name: Pancharangi
description: Bharat, played by Diganth, travels with his family to Coastal Karnataka to look for a bride for his elder brother; an arrangement made by the family members. Over the span of two days, a ...                See full summary »

name: Paramathma
description: Param (Puneeth Rajakumat), son of heart specialist Jayanth, is eager to know many things in life. He keeps shuffling from one place to another. A gold medalist in Bachelor of Science takes ...                See full summary »

description: A chef and a scientist fall in love as an epidemic begins to rob people of their sensory perceptions.

name: Rio
description: When Blu, a domesticated macaw from small-town Minnesota, meets the fiercely independent Jewel, he takes off on an adventure to Rio de Janeiro with the bird of his dreams.

name: Sanju Weds Geetha
description: Sanju Weds Geetha begins with Sanju graduating in computer science with top marks, immediately after which he leaves to his native, Kodagu. There he meets Geetha who is seen helping a ...                See full summary »

description: Manja who has been sentenced to 30 days in prison escapes just a day before his sentence officially ends after hearing that his sweetheart, Shyloo, is about to be married off to a rich guy.

name: Source Code

name: Super 8

name: Holy Motors

Six youngsters go for a trekking trip. If five of them gets killed by unknown forces, how many will return back?

name: Attahaasa

name: Case No.18/9
description: Add a Plot

description: A story about a person who brings four unknown as his family. How it unfolds is the story

stars: Samuel L. Jackson ,Kurt Russell ,Jennifer Jason Leigh

name: Annihilation

name: Call Me by Your Name

stars: Andrew Simpson ,Joséphine de La Baume ,Frédéric Pierrot

Ramachandra and Janaki meet up 20 years after graduating high school, class of 1999, at a reunion party.

name: Gentleman
description: The movie "GENTLEMAN" revolves around the character Bharath who is suffering from a rare disorder called Beauty of sleeping syndrome. Because of this, he tends to sleep 18 hours a day and ...                See full summary »

description: A detective investigates the death of the patriarch of an eccentric, combative family.

description: When a pilot crashes and tells of conflict in the outside world, Diana, an Amazonian warrior in training, leaves home to fight a war, discovering her full powers and true destiny.

name: A Beautiful Day in the Neighborhood
description: Based on the true story of a real-life friendship between Fred Rogers and journalist Lloyd Vogel.

name: Game Night
description: A group of friends who meet regularly for game nights find themselves entangled in a real-life mystery when the shady brother of one of them is seemingly kidnapped by dangerous gangsters.

name: Bramhachari
description: The film addresses sexual problems without the jokes being crass at any point.

name: Love Mocktail
description: Adi embarks on a rollercoaster journey searching for true love. Through varied experiences he questions if he'll find his soulmate.

name: Haunt

name: The Hunt
description: Twelve strangers wake up in a clearing. They don't know where they are, or how they got there. They don't know they've been chosen - for a very specific purpose - The Hunt.

name: Just Mercy
description: World-renowned civil rights defense attorney Bryan Stevenson works to free a wrongly condemned death row prisoner.

name: Polar

name: Late Night

description: Nothing in Cassie's life is what it appears to be - she's wickedly smart, tantalizingly cunning, and she's living a secret double life. Now, an unexpected encounter is about to give Cassie a chance to right the wrongs from the past.

name: Palm Springs

name: Boss Level

name: Busanhaeng

name: Godzilla vs. Kong

name: Host

name: Nobody

name: Jojo Rabbit

name: Baby Driver
